          "Background information is one-hot encoded so that, for each student-course pair, there is a OHE vector. \n\nLMS data is passed through 3 LSTMs  and the resulting state is used to create an Attention Layer.\n\nThese are concatenated and then passed through a Fully connected layer before outputting a prediction.",
